<h3>Paragraphs</h3>
<p>
    A paragraph (from the Greek paragraphos, \u201cto write beside\u201d or
    \u201cwritten beside\u201d) is a self-contained unit of a discourse in
    writing dealing with a particular point or idea. A paragraph consists of one
    or more sentences. Though not required by the syntax of any language,
    paragraphs are usually an expected part of formal writing, used to organize
    longer prose.
</p>
